title: Tajikistan Money Supply M1
description: Money Supply M1 in Tajikistan increased to 28928.60 TJS Thousand in August from 28353.84 TJS Thousand in July of 2022. Money Supply M1 in Tajikistan averaged 5752.22 TJS Thousand from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 28928.60 TJS Thousand in August of 2022 and a record low of 93.87 TJS Thousand in January of 2001. This page provides - Tajikistan Money Supply M1 - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: National Bank Of Tajikistan
